description:
WARNING THIS VIDEO IS NOT FOR THE FAINT OF HEART

Before anybody asks, yes. This is a 100% story. I once went to a Sonic Underground panel at a convention where I got to talk with some of the voice actors and other people who worked on the show.  They told me this story and told me that besides each other, I was the only person they ever told.

Jaleel White, voice actor of Sonic, Manic, and Sonia told me that he would often have a drwhile working on the show where red manic would try and beat his ass, but luckily he would always wake up because red manic could do anything to him. 

I told them that the secret was safe with me although I did ask if I could make a youtube video about it someday when I was bored and they gave me the go ahead.
